    <h1>Programmatic SEO</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of generating hundreds or thousands of search-optimized pages from templates and data at scale. Zapier ranks for <strong>1.2 million+ keywords</strong> this way — without writing each page manually.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
